<figureCitation box="[1088,1171,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–12" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1911,1935]" captionTargetBox="[156,1428,314,1884]" captionTargetId="figure-94@2.[151,1436,306,1885]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–12. Neurotettix spinas sp. nov. 1. Male habitus, dorsal view; 2. Male habitus, lateral view; 3. Face; 4. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 5. Head and thorax, lateral view; 6. Male pygofer, lateral view; 7. Genital valve; 8. left subgenital plate, ventral view; 9. Aedeagus, ventral view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Connective, dorsal view; 12. Left style, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4435676" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4435676/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="143">Fig. 12</figureCitation>
